'''Togrev the Magnificent''' was the so-called lord high commander of the armed forces of the Barony of [[Pundaria]]&mdash;although this fact was disputed.
{{Quote|I do the talking here. I am Togrev the Magnificent, lord high commander of the armed forces of [[Pundaria]]! We claim these lands by ancient right, as approved and attested by [[Zazesspur]].}}
{{TOC limit|3}}
